snippet.title: Deltarune Chapter 2 Trailer!
snippet.description:
FULL PLAYTHROUGH HERE - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lrry6GPK2_U
DELTARUNE CHAPTER 2 IS FINALLY HERE! Releasing on the 17th September! GET FREAKING HYPED!
Deltarune is Toby Fox's newest masterpiece! A Sequel to Undertale! Undertale 2, if you will, except it's called Deltarune! 
Deltarune Chapter 2 will continue where we left off and I'm sure ask a lot more questions as the game answers a couple of our existing ones.

HUGE thanks to my Master Tier or higher supporters on Patreon:
Daniel Pace (dcp1992)
Sarah Essex
TARDIS Type40
Holmes_Watson2011
WrathChild1995
Luke Seymour
Melvin Winthagen
Kyjbuzz

I'd really appreciate it if you left a like, subscribed & clicked the notification bell!
